351
00:20:47,606 --> 00:20:51,308
This is what we call human-centered design.

352
00:20:51,308 --> 00:20:53,169
We make sure that it's usable,

353
00:20:53,169 --> 00:20:54,971
so that we understand the sense and feedback,

