00:20:54,971 --> 00:20:58,713
that we understand how to use the system.

355
00:20:58,713 --> 00:21:00,274
We have form follows function,

356
00:21:00,274 --> 00:21:02,716
function comes first, and we try to make sure

357
00:21:02,716 --> 00:21:05,037
that the functionality is conveyed

358
00:21:05,037 --> 00:21:08,299
through the shape and sound of the element.

359
00:21:09,225 --> 00:21:15,251
All of these things is about behavioral level and of course accessibility is in there.

360
00:21:16,788 --> 00:21:19,189
And the last level is reflective.

361
00:21:19,189 --> 00:21:23,132
So this is more about the self-image

362
00:21:23,132 --> 00:21:26,314
that we get when we interact with the system.

363
00:21:26,314 --> 00:21:30,657
Maybe we felt guilt or maybe we are proud because we won.

