00:21:59,702 --> 00:22:02,603
So it's all about the story, the narrative,

375
00:22:02,603 --> 00:22:07,804
the meaning, what does it mean to you?

376
00:22:07,804 --> 00:22:10,565
So it's not now, not about the functionality,

377
00:22:10,565 --> 00:22:12,165
but it's about how you reflect.

378
00:22:13,106 --> 00:22:20,869
on this. Novelty is also a part of it. We like to have novel experiences, and so we

379
00:22:20,869 --> 00:22:28,692
can reflect on these elements. So this is the baseline, the three levels of process

380
00:22:28,692 --> 00:22:33,854
when we interact with anything. So these all happen at the same time, and this was very

